<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هِيَ الدُّنْيَا قِتَالٌ نَحْنُ فِيهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مَقَاصِدُ لِلْحِسَانِ وَلِلْقَنَاتِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span> ... لَعَمْرُكَ مَا حَيُّ وَإِنْ طَالَ سَيْرُهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يُعَدُّ طَلِيقًا وَالْمَنُونُ لَهُ أَسْرُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلا تَحْسَبَنَّ الْمَرْءَ فِيهَا بِخَالِدٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلَكِنَّهُ يَسْعَى وَغَايَتُهُ الْقَبْرُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span> ... قِفْ بِالْقُبُور وَنَادِ الْمُسْتَقِرَّ بِهَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مِنْ أَعْظُمٍ بَلَيْتَ فِيهَا وَأَجْسَادِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>قَوْمٌ تَقَطَّعَتِ الأَسْبَابُ بَيْنَهُوا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بَعْدَ الْوِصَالِ فَصَارُوا تَحْتَ أَلْحَادِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَاللهُ لَوْ بُعْثَرُوا يَوْمًا وَلَوْ نُشِرُوا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قَالُوا بِأَنَّ التُّقَى مِنْ أَعْظِمِ الزَّادِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span> ... نُراعُ لِذِكْرِ الْمَوْتِ سَاعَةَ ذِكْرِهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَتَعْتَرِضُ الدُّنْيَا فَنَلهُوا وَنَلْعَبُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَقِينٌ كَأَنَّ الشَّكَّ غَالِبُ أَمْرِهِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>عَلَيْهِ وَعِرْفَانُ إِلَى الْجَهْلِ يُنْسَبُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span> ... وَدُنْيَاكَ الَّتِي غَرَّتْكَ مِنْهَا ... زَخَارِفُهَا تَصِيرُ إِلَى انْجِذَاذِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تَزَحْزَحْ عَنْ مَهَالِكِهَا بِجُهْدٍ ... فَمَا أَصْغَى إِلَيْهَا ذُو نَفَاذِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>